How do you manage your bookmarks?
 This is a regular question usually from new team members for the past ten years or so. My answer has been the same, &ldquo;I use a tool I wrote.&rdquo; followed by, &ldquo;I will send you the LAN location where I have saved it. You can use it from there or just make a copy of your own.&rdquo;
I remember myself asking that question to others when I first started the job in mid 2000s.
